column1: Following query was issued to GS:
Possibilities of improving properties of microalloyed steel weld metal by choice of welding process and technology
column2: R Prokić-Cvetković, O Popović, R Jovičić… - … associated technology …, 2011 - tmt.unze.ba
column12: In this paper is shown the influence of welding process and technology on the weld metal properties. Microalloyed steel, low alloyed by Ti, Nb and V, is welded by MMA process and MIG/MAG process in the shielding atmospheres 5% CO2+ Ar and 15% CO2+ Ar. The testing …
